{"tid":2332192,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"鋼琴女神李元玲急刪走光相　重po性感相兼有火藥味？","createTime":"2020-12-19T12:01:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-19T13:50:08.000Z","uid":164938,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"9c45fb05ca15d12194e840581a199800c2df56da","tid":2332192,"uid":164938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T12:01:04.000Z","msg":"來自馬來西亞的「鋼琴女神」李元玲除了擁有高超琴技，還擁有Fit爆身材，向來都大方地向網民、粉絲大騷其巨乳、纖腰與長腿，她日前就照樣分享自己的性感相，不過由於火紅色低胸吊帶裙過短再加上她烏身向前傾，就令她不慎露出白色內褲，雖然不是嚴重地「露點」，但始終都是一張走光相，又有網民拍相片太過火，李元玲當時就馬上刪去該則帖文！<br />\n<br />\n李元玲的Instagram內已沒有原圖存在，換成兩張相同打扮的相，而她在其中一張相當中都有用手拉著短裙，是用相片來證明自己有小心注意嗎？李元玲又似是對網民的爭論略有不滿，就在帖文留下一句「吵死了，可以了嘛這樣？」不過有部份網民就揚言自己早已把走光Cap圖儲存，未知會否再引起一輪罵戰呢？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://ent.fanpiece.com/m/smalleyesentertainment/c1391386.html?page=fanpiece&amp;fbclid=IwAR3QPnZAWkilUEpkgqVQuKGmSCSbsPhSLdjxZTsVNEBIsM6ACMe4SFtY_to\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fent.fanpiece.com%2Fm%2Fsmalleyesentertainment%2Fc1391386.html%3Fpage%3Dfanpiece%26fbclid%3DIwAR3QPnZAWkilUEpkgqVQuKGmSCSbsPhSLdjxZTsVNEBIsM6ACMe4SFtY_to&d=XkDMRo5st5VLQkVJYuplWCukga04qSQtFIF%2FU0RrEoA%3D&h=5af84a07\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ent.fanpiece.com/m/smalleyesentertainment/c1391386.html?page=fanpiece&amp;fbclid=IwAR3QPnZAWkilUEpkgqVQuKGmSCSbsPhSLdjxZTsVNEBIsM6ACMe4SFtY_to</a>"},{"pid":"ac847b795b7e50e494a6b7978f0b3052a1ccc8c4","tid":2332192,"uid":201512,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T12:03:37.000Z","msg":"hi<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我入黎係睇梁家輝gif架<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"428a02508d047e539751d60276e9ab9c717bbe2a","tid":2332192,"uid":41368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T12:03:46.000Z","msg":"咁走光圖呢"},{"pid":"b0c8eb08514391900c465b9ed14af98a80f29505","tid":2332192,"uid":371175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-